name: Russborough
info: This week's race will be 4 separate races on the Russborough circuit. The number of laps will be decided on the night
The finish line is off the circuit on the road up to Russborough house, roughly 300m. We'll be on the turn every lap and you'll get a bell on your final lap
Sign on location in Blessington industrial estate
Sign on will close at 6.50pm, first group off at 7pm
